{"tid":761973,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都係好遲鈍？","createTime":"2018-07-31T00:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T04:49:00.000Z","uid":197135,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a510510a6a5db07e6066201b2f74108edf99d7","tid":761973,"uid":197135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:50:52.000Z","msg":"我就係，唔好點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人串我都唔知，例如我同屋企人傾話有個舊時女明星好靚女啦，跟住講講下，佢無啦啦話&rdquo;你咁鍾意佢，佢放個屁你都覺得香啦&rdquo; 跟住我就覺得搵到知音同好咁 覺得佢明白我有幾鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後隔咗一個月我諗返個對話先覺得有啲唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有就係曾經中學個陣有個人鍾意我，其實都表現得好明顯了，但我一直都唔知，直至兩年之後，我個朋友話我知，我先醒覺，鍾意我個個女仔曾經wts約我出街，佢話想一齊溫書，跟住我就諗自己溫書入腦啲就唔去了，依家諗返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得自己好蠢  抵forever a0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我個人唔會成日諗呢啲愛情野 所以唔係好接到啲signal <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩法子可以醒目啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人串都唔知真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50aefab844e6486e78eb7feb76c1ecb6c0f97a61","tid":761973,"uid":132674,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:54:59.000Z","msg":"咁都有女鐘意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df95e59d13806ac39d00226b4cae76a518a995a","tid":761973,"uid":197135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50aefab844e6486e78eb7feb76c1ecb6c0f97a61","tid":761973,"uid":132674,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:54:59.000Z","msg":"咁都有女鐘意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9ccb56292dc4142af6ceba604aaadfc5936378","tid":761973,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T01:00:58.000Z","msg":"蠢既人唔會醒架喇，但就由以往被串既經驗度學習囉<br />\n<br />\n即係同一樣野唔好俾人串第二次都唔識醒<br />\n<br />\n同埋要受教，人地教你你真係要學<br />\n<br />\n以前都有個朋友好撚柒蠢，真係蠢到佢自己都周圍認果隻<br />\n<br />\n仆街次次教佢D野果陣就唔撚學，之後又唔撚識又搵勁多借口，咁直頭係蠢到好乞人憎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afa954c9264c7579d1919343ad97bc1fccc6184","tid":761973,"uid":197135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c9ccb56292dc4142af6ceba604aaadfc5936378","tid":761973,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T01:00:58.000Z","msg":"蠢既人唔會醒架喇，但就由以往被串既經驗度學習囉<br />\n<br />\n即係同一樣野唔好俾人串第二次都唔識醒<br />\n<br />\n同埋要受教，人地教你你真係要學<br />\n<br />\n以前都有個朋友好撚柒蠢，真係蠢到佢自己都周圍認果隻<br />\n<br />\n仆街次次教佢D野果陣就唔撚學，之後又唔撚識又搵勁多借口，咁直頭係蠢到好乞人憎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T01:06:27.000Z","msg":"Thx bro 同一樣野下次唔會再犯 但好多次都會有新既野出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蠢既人真係永遠都係蠢嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059d34966cfffbdd350d42df3b36cf47d26e440a","tid":761973,"uid":197135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T01:09:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676e64c07cd90ee422523ec1de8fdb2000cb39a3","tid":761973,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3afa954c9264c7579d1919343ad97bc1fccc6184","tid":761973,"uid":197135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c9ccb56292dc4142af6ceba604aaadfc5936378","tid":761973,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T01:00:58.000Z","msg":"蠢既人唔會醒架喇，但就由以往被串既經驗度學習囉<br />\n<br />\n即係同一樣野唔好俾人串第二次都唔識醒<br />\n<br />\n同埋要受教，人地教你你真係要學<br />\n<br />\n以前都有個朋友好撚柒蠢，真係蠢到佢自己都周圍認果隻<br />\n<br />\n仆街次次教佢D野果陣就唔撚學，之後又唔撚識又搵勁多借口，咁直頭係蠢到好乞人憎 <img src=\"/asset